<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>写程序的龙龙 (Posts about Raspberry)</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/categories/raspberry.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 27 Feb 2017 18:44:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>Raspberry设置静态IP</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/raspberryshe-zhi-jing-tai-ip/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;1、编辑网络配置文件。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;pre class="literal-block"&gt;
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; sudo vi /etc/network/interfaces
iface eth0 inet static
address 192.168.1.254
netmask 255.255.255.0
gateway 192.168.1.1
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; sudo service networking restart
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、重启系统和路由器。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;如果不行的话，试试把路由器也设置成静态地址绑定……&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>Linux</category><category>Raspberry</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/raspberryshe-zhi-jing-tai-ip/</guid><pubDate>Mon, 27 Feb 2017 11:45:07 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>